  {
    "id": "purchases-invoicing-payment-methods",
    "title": "What payment methods do you accept?",
    "description": "What payment methods does SlideHeroes support??",
    "content": {
      "root": {
        "type": "root",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "version": 1,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Currently, SlideHeroes supports several different payment methods, depending on\nyour account country and location."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "This article outlines how you can confirm\nwhich payment methods are available to you, when you go to purchase a course."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "The following are the payment methods we support today:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "**International Credit and Debit Cards:**"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "We accept most major international credit and debit cards like Visa, MasterCard, American Express, JCB and Discover."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "PayPal is a supported method of payment for SlideHeroes courses in most countries."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "For Teams we support ACH Bank Transfers globally. If there is a payment method that we do not support that you require, please reach out to SlideHeroes Support."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "slug": "purchases-invoicing/payment-methods",
    "order": 312,
    "featured": false,
    "tags": [],
    "breadcrumbs": [
      {
        "title": "Purchases Invoicing",
        "slug": "purchases-invoicing"
      },
      {
        "title": "What payment methods do you accept?",
        "slug": "purchases-invoicing/payment-methods"
      }
