  {
    "id": "refunds-refund-policy",
    "title": "Our Refund Policy",
    "description": "Our Refund Policy",
    "content": {
      "root": {
        "type": "root",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "version": 1,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "We want you to be satisfied, so all eligible courses purchased on Udemy can be\nrefunded within 30 days, provided the request meets the guidelines in our refund\npolicy. ## How to submit a refund request Learn how to submit a refund request…\n[Read more](/docs/overview). ## Our 30-day policy While our 30-day refund policy\nis to allow students to learn risk free, we also must protect against fraud. We\nwill not process refund requests received after the refund window. ## Additional\nreasons for denied refunds We reserve the right, in our sole discretion, to\nlimit or deny refund requests in cases where we believe there is refund abuse,\nincluding but not limited to the following: - A significant portion of the\ncourse has been consumed or downloaded by a student before the refund was\nrequested. - Multiple refunds have been requested by a student for the same\ncourse. - Excessive refunds have been requested by a student. - We do not grant\nrefunds for any subscription services unless otherwise required by applicable\nlaw (please see below for more information). These refund restrictions will be\nenforced to the extent permitted by applicable law. ## Refund requests for\ncourses purchased with an academic discount We do not provide refunds on\nSlideHeroes courses purchased with an academic discount that are part of a\nuniversity or college course."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "slug": "refunds/refund-policy",
    "order": 314,
    "featured": false,
    "tags": [],
    "breadcrumbs": [
      {
        "title": "Refunds",
        "slug": "refunds"
      },
      {
        "title": "Our Refund Policy",
        "slug": "refunds/refund-policy"
      }
    ],
    "published": true,
    "createdAt": "2025-10-03T20:57:57.725Z",
    "updatedAt": "2025-10-03T20:57:57.725Z",
    "category": "Refunds"
  },
  {
    "id": "refunds-refund-process",
    "title": "Refund Process",
    "description": "How to request a refund",
    "content": {
      "root": {
        "type": "root",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "version": 1,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "We want you to be satisfied, so all eligible courses purchased from SlideHeroes can be refunded within 30 days."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "For whatever reason, if you are unhappy with a course, you can request a refund, provided the request meets the guidelines in our [refund policy](/refund-policy)"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Most refunds are returned via the original payment method. Please note that certain restrictions may apply and some purchases may only be eligible for credit refunds."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "tag": "h2",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "How to request a refund:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "listType": "bullet",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "listitem",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Review our [Refund Policy](/refund-policy)"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "listitem",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "If your purchase data is within 30 days, forward your purchase receipt to support@slideheroes.com"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "listitem",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "We will respond with confirmation of a refund within 24 hours."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "slug": "refunds/refund-process",
    "order": 314,
    "featured": false,
    "tags": [],
    "breadcrumbs": [
      {
        "title": "Refunds",
        "slug": "refunds"
      },
      {
        "title": "Refund Process",
        "slug": "refunds/refund-process"
      }
    ],
