              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "MakerKit uses Supabase to manage authentication within your application. By\ndefault, every kit comes with the following built-in authentication methods: -\n**Email/Password** - we added, by default, the traditional way of signing in -\n**Third Party Providers** - we also added by default Google Auth sign-in -\n**Email Links** - **Phone Number** You're free to add (or remove) any of the\nmethods supported by Supabase's Authentication: we will see how."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
